   <body>
      <p>When an agreement is first created, the agreement status is In Request. When a program is created from the agreement, its status is set to Draft.</p>
      <p>After reviewing the agreement and program, Program analysts activate the agreement: this also activates any program associated to the agreement. Agreement and Program statuses are set to Activated.</p>
